# Raw pasta with sauce

This is a great recipe. 

## Pasta

3 spiralised zucchini (medium)

## Sauce

350g Tomatoes
300g Capsicum
50g Paprika
2 dates
80g Basil
1/2C olive oil

## Topping

30g broken cashew nuts
20 olives
20g basil (chopped)
30g capers

## Instructions

Spiralise the zucchini. Blend the sauce, pour it on the zucchini. Add topping.

